Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.92,0:00:21.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 身為妖精的我們
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.76,0:00:23.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然要乘坐這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.43,0:00:26.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有在聽嗎 諾瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.12,0:00:28.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦? 啊 恩…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.30,0:00:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常愜意
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.18,0:00:36.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說呢 跟戰士長一起 這樣也很不錯哩
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.61,0:00:38.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.71,0:00:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Queen's Blade 結束後的現如今
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.36,0:00:45.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,本應該立刻返回妖精森林去的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.51,0:00:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而順從了諾瓦的願望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.15,0:00:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微繞了點遠路
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.96,0:00:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,確實 再保持一直以來的死板想法的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.76,0:00:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就真的和長老們沒有區別了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.09,0:01:01.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.13,0:01:06.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓要妖精族的長老們  認同諾瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.92,0:01:11.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰士…長
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.36,0:01:22.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰士長
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.32,0:01:36.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾瓦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.60,0:01:40.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沼地魔女的威脅尚未消失
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.66,0:01:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這般玩樂的同時
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.73,0:01:44.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好大
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.52,0:01:46.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定妖精之森已經陷入了危機之中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.47,0:01:47.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰士長 快來這邊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.31,0:01:53.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我認為新女王會去討伐沼地魔女
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.90,0:01:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但卻沒有絕對的保證
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.41,0:02:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也聽說過有人在襲擊鬥士這樣的傳言
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.89,0:02:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不能太悠閒了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.29,0:02:12.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 諾瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.45,0:02:13.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,稍微…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.20,0:02:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼事 戰士長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.51,0:02:19.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾瓦！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.06,0:02:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 啊咧咧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.23,0:02:28.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,使不上力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.20,0:02:30.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真拿你沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.52,0:02:35.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從無法好好計算剩餘體力這點看來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.44,0:02:39.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,緊要關頭時可無法派上用場
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.02,0:02:41.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾瓦 20分
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.51,0:02:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾瓦？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.98,0:02:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰士長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.44,0:02:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真大啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.19,0:03:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是大海嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.33,0:03:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.37,0:03:04.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是第一次看到海對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.01,0:03:04.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.84,0:03:08.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定會去海邊玩玩的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.69,0:03:08.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.17,0:03:10.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.04,0:03:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不想想我們繞了多少遠路
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.45,0:03:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾瓦 站住
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.18,0:03:25.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好寬 好廣 好壯麗 大海啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.04,0:03:42.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰士長
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.40,0:03:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋 哪有人會裸奔下去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.92,0:03:49.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且下水前還要先做熱身運動才行
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.75,0:03:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？ 好鹹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.99,0:03:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這水好鹹啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.24,0:03:57.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂的海水就是那樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.60,0:04:02.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾瓦 待在那別動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.85,0:04:06.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Eagle Cannon
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.68,0:04:13.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打偏了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.29,0:04:25.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把…把這穿上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.52,0:04:26.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.58,0:04:31.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種東西不穿也沒關係的嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.00,0:04:36.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好了 這裡跟妖精森林的泉水可不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.21,0:04:38.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿好了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.69,0:04:41.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 很好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.51,0:04:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論如何都不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.02,0:04:46.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.87,0:04:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論 無論如何都不行？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.97,0:04:52.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這麼不聽話還真是少見啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.58,0:04:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也許…吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.58,0:05:02.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.18,0:05:06.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是休息一晚的話 或許也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.65,0:05:07.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.74,0:05:08.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.65,0:05:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了 休息一晚對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.11,0:05:14.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說好了 明天就出發回妖精森林
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.85,0:05:43.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.19,0:06:00.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,危險 戰士長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.57,0:06:08.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.68,0:06:17.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不放水的喲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.38,0:06:20.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贏了鬥士 名利雙收的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.01,0:06:22.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很厲害吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.86,0:06:25.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會厲害到飛起耶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.07,0:06:28.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對我們不需要手下留情 來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.33,0:06:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就上了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.39,0:06:31.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.11,0:06:39.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃電發球
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.06,0:06:47.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過去了 諾瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.78,0:06:51.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 去了 戰士長
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.67,0:06:52.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.92,0:06:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.26,0:07:00.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的 坑爹呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.07,0:07:02.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好棒 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.48,0:07:05.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的行動也不錯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.66,0:07:07.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾瓦 70分
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.30,0:07:08.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的嗎 真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.58,0:07:14.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 戰鬥還沒結束
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.70,0:07:15.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要掉以輕心 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.86,0:07:17.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該你們了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.36,0:07:24.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是什麼呢 這種感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.18,0:07:30.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明我必須回妖精森林才行的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.16,0:07:37.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,守護妖精森林才是我的使命 是內心的喜悅
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.91,0:07:43.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…是什麼呢…這內心的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.42,0:07:47.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常的幸福與滿足
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.72,0:07:51.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆就這樣跟諾瓦…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.97,0:08:03.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露 沒問題 一定能找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.56,0:08:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了 諾瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.81,0:08:14.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海裡有什麼東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.78,0:08:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰士長 你還記得嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.09,0:08:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什麼 不提了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.20,0:08:26.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾瓦 那個球是剛才的…？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.84,0:08:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 在暗處會隱約發光
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.62,0:08:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.13,0:08:33.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睡吧 戰士長
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.14,0:08:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久以前 戰士長曾告訴過我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.25,0:08:48.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這片海底存在著不可思議的石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.98,0:08:51.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是叫思念石來著？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.70,0:09:07.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,噓… 不瞞著戰士長就沒意義了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.52,0:09:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們運氣好過頭了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.30,0:09:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊對啊 好的沒話說 多到爆啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.24,0:09:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那不是鬥士大人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.82,0:09:32.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大半夜的搞啥飛機呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.60,0:09:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰知道 搞不懂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.97,0:09:41.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太暗找不到呢 露
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.88,0:09:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然不潛下去不行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.57,0:10:41.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.09,0:10:48.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.42,0:10:50.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底去哪兒了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.88,0:11:18.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼了 諾瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.21,0:11:23.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兒怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.79,0:11:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我勒個擦 勝利之風竟然斷了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.46,0:11:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡 讓它逃掉了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.18,0:11:44.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.94,0:11:50.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 鬥士大人 太謝謝你了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.83,0:11:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先別管我…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.10,0:12:01.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像沒有大礙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.73,0:12:02.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.05,0:12:05.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 我正在找我的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.88,0:12:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 她的話剛剛往巖壁去了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.80,0:12:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巖壁？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.04,0:12:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.74,0:12:14.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要去那種地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.84,0:12:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊的海流會隨時間突然改變 超危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.74,0:12:22.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且聽說魔物經常會在那裡出現
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.47,0:12:23.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是剛才那傢伙嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.53,0:12:23.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.28,0:12:26.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可不是鬧著玩的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.90,0:12:30.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露 你在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.71,0:12:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾瓦 你在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.28,0:12:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露 諾瓦在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.40,0:12:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那球…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.36,0:12:42.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.77,0:12:54.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾瓦 你在哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.73,0:12:56.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該不會被魔物給…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.89,0:13:00.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,何等失態 何等怠慢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.69,0:13:06.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是以前的我 怎麼可能覺察不到魔物的氣息
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.74,0:13:09.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是丟妖精族戰鬥教官的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.75,0:13:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,根本就不該在這種地方悠然自得
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.75,0:13:18.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明清楚這點 卻還…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.59,0:13:38.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水流好像變緩了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.98,0:13:42.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡到底是哪兒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.00,0:13:49.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像是在島的後方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.94,0:13:52.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.46,0:13:54.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有濕
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.43,0:13:57.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,退潮後地面露出來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.46,0:14:01.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾瓦就在附近
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.61,0:14:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可千萬別出事了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.25,0:14:09.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露 不好意思 把衣服給我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.85,0:14:14.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快吃了東西 讓身子暖和起來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.02,0:14:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 謝謝你
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.95,0:14:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能合你胃口的話就再好不過了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.89,0:14:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃 這是妮庫絲小姐做的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.26,0:14:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.91,0:14:30.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道是不是因遭到海浪蹂躪的關係
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.33,0:14:32.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從海藻中可以煮出不少湯汁
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.47,0:14:37.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮庫絲小姐真是厲害呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.29,0:14:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我還差得遠呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.18,0:14:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有弗尼庫拉大人在 我才能辦到
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.82,0:14:45.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正在熟睡之中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.91,0:14:57.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那把杖還是丟掉比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.44,0:14:57.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.63,0:15:00.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給人一種不祥的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.13,0:15:01.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮庫絲小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.29,0:15:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一直拿著那把杖是不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.19,0:15:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 沒有弗尼庫拉大人在 我就什麼也做不瞭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.02,0:15:11.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.54,0:15:14.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮庫絲小姐不是能做出這麼好吃的料理嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.94,0:15:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.91,0:15:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾瓦 叫我好找啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.63,0:15:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰士長
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.20,0:15:30.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 濕透了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.76,0:15:31.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,露
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.17,0:15:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真想不到你會在這種地方悠閒地吃著飯啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.12,0:15:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮庫絲小姐請我吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.55,0:15:38.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火焰使 妮庫絲
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.29,0:15:41.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的魔物 是你的把戲嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.24,0:15:42.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,唉？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.89,0:15:45.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮庫絲小姐一直跟諾瓦在一起啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.47,0:15:46.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要被騙了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.54,0:15:48.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔物正是那把名為弗尼庫拉的杖
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.03,0:15:53.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮庫絲只不過是個被杖給操控了的內心軟弱之人罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.28,0:15:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.23,0:15:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮庫絲小姐待人非常親切 非常的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.69,0:16:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要回妖精森林了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.67,0:16:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在立刻出發
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.26,0:16:06.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是戰士長你全身都濕透了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.49,0:16:07.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不趕快曬乾的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.67,0:16:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.32,0:16:09.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出發了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.52,0:16:10.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可…可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.85,0:16:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.74,0:16:17.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不介意的話 喝碗熱海藻湯再走如何呢…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.43,0:16:19.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你照顧諾瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.52,0:16:23.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我可不想跟魔物打交道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.11,0:16:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.01,0:16:25.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰士長…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.12,0:16:29.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的使命是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.63,0:16:32.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我 吾之徒弟
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.81,0:16:34.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,森林的守門人 諾瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.74,0:16:37.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩耍的時間已經結束了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.04,0:16:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.62,0:17:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗尼庫拉大人
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.69,0:17:04.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.45,0:17:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮庫絲小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.41,0:17:09.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢著 諾瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.26,0:17:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾瓦 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.59,0:17:15.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.69,0:17:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要弄出好湯汁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.44,0:17:23.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,火候可是比什麼都重要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.04,0:17:25.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮庫絲小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.91,0:17:29.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然不肯吃我這個正義的火焰使
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.65,0:17:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮庫絲大人親手做的料理！？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.78,0:17:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要大意了 諾瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.57,0:17:42.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.80,0:17:45.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個傢伙也是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.88,0:17:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對弗尼庫拉大人說這說那的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.82,0:17:53.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上是想從我身邊奪走弗尼庫拉大人對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.75,0:17:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這樣的 諾瓦我只是…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.62,0:17:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.51,0:18:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰士長
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.36,0:18:08.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要慌張
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.35,0:18:10.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不過是在重複單調的攻擊而已
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.12,0:18:12.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,久而久之自然會露出破綻的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.03,0:18:14.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那時便是取勝的時機
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.51,0:18:14.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.53,0:18:31.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.20,0:18:36.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.08,0:18:40.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.18,0:18:43.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.36,0:18:47.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是愚蠢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.83,0:18:48.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.51,0:18:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那並非你自身的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.49,0:18:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟連其是邪惡魔物之力都覺察不到
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.41,0:19:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,囉哩八嗦 嘰嘰歪歪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.67,0:19:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.41,0:19:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仰仗弗尼庫拉大人又有何錯
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.96,0:19:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟因此就能變強 老娘是最強的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.74,0:19:20.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是可悲 沒有依靠就無法生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.56,0:19:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hurricane Fury
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.04,0:19:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰士長 小心背後
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.11,0:19:54.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗尼庫拉大人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.63,0:19:55.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.47,0:19:58.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種人更好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.35,0:20:03.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要你的 明明是我
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.34,0:20:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.52,0:20:07.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成是想對我進行附體
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.67,0:20:29.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.59,0:20:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的心靈正被逐漸侵蝕…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.54,0:20:36.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.67,0:20:41.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我難道今後想活下去就必須要有所依靠了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.47,0:20:43.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.75,0:20:45.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕不…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.09,0:20:47.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.57,0:20:56.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰士長
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.31,0:20:59.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾瓦…諾瓦…諾瓦…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.33,0:21:02.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.02,0:21:07.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快給我… 放開戰士長！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.97,0:21:15.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗尼庫拉大人！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.98,0:21:19.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮庫絲小姐 其實大家都是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.86,0:21:21.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一個人的話會感到孤單
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.85,0:21:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不依靠別人就無法生活下去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.39,0:21:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 總有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.62,0:21:28.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要獨立的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.49,0:21:31.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終將會來臨的！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.82,0:21:34.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.82,0:21:41.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弗尼庫拉大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.45,0:21:51.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妮庫絲小姐 走了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.20,0:22:00.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我忘了我不會游泳了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.35,0:22:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰來救救我 拜託了…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.47,0:22:22.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從在妖精森林跟諾瓦相遇起
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.42,0:22:26.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至今為止 我總是優先考慮諾瓦的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.94,0:22:31.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總是認為諾瓦還需要我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.03,0:22:33.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如此堅信著
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.78,0:22:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然而…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.14,0:22:38.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,事實上並非如此
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.27,0:22:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是我
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.29,0:22:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.43,0:22:44.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實是我需要著你
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.16,0:22:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不需要任何話語
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.98,0:22:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.13,0:22:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說不定跟妮庫絲一樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.01,0:22:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都無法獨自生活
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.62,0:22:57.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不依靠別人就無法生活下去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.54,0:22:59.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 總有一天
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.70,0:23:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,需要獨立的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.40,0:23:04.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,終將會來臨的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.28,0:23:07.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰士長
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.27,0:23:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們在此說再見吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.65,0:23:12.20,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.48,0:23:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果回到森林的話會給我帶去麻煩
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.01,0:23:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你的理由嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.62,0:23:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有這方面的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.99,0:23:21.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但不全是
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.66,0:23:24.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟大家相遇後我才發覺
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.55,0:23:26.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蕾娜也好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.68,0:23:27.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,艾基多娜小姐也好
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.11,0:23:30.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在Queen's Blade中遇到的大家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.40,0:23:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都不依賴著他人而獨立生活著
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.17,0:23:38.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想一個人看看更為廣闊的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.54,0:23:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從何時起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.93,0:23:42.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就開始這麼想了？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.88,0:23:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這次的旅途之中 下定的決心
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.12,0:23:47.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.97,0:23:52.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以最後我想把這個送給戰士長
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.42,0:23:55.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.53,0:23:56.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,思念石
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.72,0:24:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在手中將其握熱 就能見到最為思念之人的身影
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.83,0:24:05.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以前戰士長跟我這樣說過
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.43,0:24:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然…還記得呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.27,0:24:12.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也是我開始搜集石頭的契機
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.13,0:24:16.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且戰士長說過的話 諾瓦是絕不會忘記的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:17.93,0:24:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.33,0:24:20.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明好不容易才找到的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.65,0:24:22.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻摔壞了
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.42,0:24:26.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算沒有這種石頭
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.19,0:24:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.33,0:24:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算沒有這種石頭…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:30.34,0:24:32.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也絕對不會忘記你的
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.71,0:24:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經活了超過千年的時光
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.42,0:24:40.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:24:40.54,0:24:42.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與你在一起的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.70,0:24:45.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卻是任何事物也無法取代的美好回憶
Dialogue: 0,0:24:46.51,0:24:48.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知不覺中
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.25,0:24:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經成長的如此出色了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:24:52.36,0:24:55.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經沒有任何東西可以教給你了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:00.41,0:25:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.50,0:25:03.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,100分
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.44,0:25:18.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,諾瓦啊 已經沒有東西可以束縛你了
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.85,0:25:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從現在開始就用你的眼睛、耳朵和心
Dialogue: 0,0:25:24.31,0:25:26.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去好好感悟更多更多的事物吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.57,0:25:32.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這廣袤的世界一定可以
Dialogue: 0,0:25:33.02,0:25:34.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,填滿你的好奇心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.01,0:25:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.42,0:25:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到時我們再在某處重逢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:25:39.40,0:25:42.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在此之前便先告別了 諾瓦
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.08,0:25:54.47,bt,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,400)\an8}不勝依依！ 艾琳千年別離
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.18,0:27:54.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咳咳…還以為我要領便當了
Dialogue: 0,0:27:54.66,0:27:56.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個死妖精真他妹的叫人火大
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.94,0:27:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊…弗…弗尼庫拉大人
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.09,0:28:00.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您沒事真是太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.13,0:28:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有弗尼庫拉大人在的話
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.82,0:28:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妖精也好 貴族也罷 還是沼地魔女 放馬過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.97,0:28:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,順便預告也放馬過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.67,0:28:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下回 憂鬱 艾莉的二心
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.65,0:28:15.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好難受… 弗尼庫拉大人
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.71,0:28:18.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請饒了我吧… 人家要丟了
































































